name: Physics Wallah
description: Physics Wallah offers comprehensive physics lectures for students preparing for competitive exams. The channel covers everything from basic concepts to advanced problem-solving with clear explanations and visual demonstrations. Perfect for JEE, NEET and board exam preparation.

name: Khan Academy
description: Khan Academy provides free world-class education for anyone, anywhere. The platform covers math, science, programming, history, and more with interactive exercises, videos, and a personalized learning dashboard. Students can learn at their own pace with step-by-step guidance.
